snippet.title: Lumberhill - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Lumberhill is a multiplayer party game where lumberjacks try to get their job done while nature fights back. Just like Tools Up!, it's an "Overcooked-like" about bonding, squabbling and progressing with teammates in a frantic, hilarious atmosphere. It features 1-4 player local and online co-op, pvp and solo modes.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
